+| `accepted_in_kb_base` | Represented in the current Hygiene Clean KB scaffold or appendix set; not promoted to global runtime truth by placement alone. |
+| `verified` | Checked against the required local evidence or target surface for the bounded task. |
+| `runtime_truth` | Accepted only through the governed promotion or managed-law path outside this KB scaffold. |
+| `promotion_required` | Cannot become accepted truth without the governed promotion route. |
+| `deferred` | Kept for future consideration, later QA, or appendix-only retention; not integrated into scaffold in this pass. |
+| `rejected` | Explicitly excluded from this KB content pass. |
 | `blocked` | Candidate cannot advance because a source, authority, or conflict issue remains unresolved. |
