+## Realization trace fields
+
+| Field | Meaning |
+|---|---|
+| `realized_as` | How the candidate is represented after this KB update pass. |
+| `realized_file` | File that receives or preserves the candidate. |
+| `scaffold_id` | Local scaffold identifier, heading, or retained pattern that represents the candidate. |
+| `status_after_build` | Post-update status using the local status vocabulary. |
+| `next_validation` | Follow-up check, validation owner, or no-op preservation note. |
