+## Runtime-truth boundary
+
+Candidate realization in this ledger means the candidate was represented, preserved, or explicitly deferred in the Hygiene Clean KB scaffold or appendices.
+
+It does not promote the candidate to runtime truth. Truth-changing use still requires governed promotion.
 
